&lt;li&gt;Strong oral and written communications skills (writing sample on request).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to take initiative, work independently, and work closely with partners in a collaborative environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
