&lt;li&gt;Serve as lead analyst and primary contact with clients, deal arrangers and investors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and present credit memoranda to rating committees and contribute to transaction reports for publication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the development of new rating methodologies (as necessary), as well as topical research and market commentaries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Surveil and monitor outstanding transactions, updating ratings as warranted.&lt;/li&gt;
