&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KBRA &lt;/strong&gt;(Kroll Bond Rating Agency, LLC).&amp;nbsp;is seeking an &lt;strong&gt;Analyst/Senior Analyst &lt;/strong&gt;to join our growing &lt;strong&gt;Funds Ratings&lt;/strong&gt; team in the &lt;strong&gt;New York&lt;/strong&gt; office. The Funds team assigns and monitors credit ratings on various debt instruments issued by funds, closed-end funds, and other fund vehicles.&amp;nbsp; KBRA’s growing ratings portfolio encompasses funds which leverage a variety of asset growth and income generation strategies including fixed income securities, private equity, private credit, real estate, and middle market lending.&amp;nbsp; A strong candidate will have extensive experience and interest in fund investment and credit strategies.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Job:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
