&lt;li&gt;Ability to work as an integral part of a highly collaborative team and across disciplines in a challenging and dynamic environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage time and resources in a fast-growing company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective verbal, written and presentation communications skills.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
